A(85~100) / B(70~84) / C(50~69) / D(30~49) / F(0~29)

## STEP 8 — diagnosis_codes
ZERO_UNRECOGNIZED / ZERO_NO_MATCH / POSSIBLE_FALLBACK / ETC_TYPE /
BRAND_MAPPING_WRONG / CATEGORY_MAPPING_WRONG / LOW_RELEVANCE /
POOR_RANKING / NO_SYNONYM / SOLDOUT_EXPOSED

