  ```
  (이미 search_keywords에 있는 경우 발골 사전 매핑만 추가)

- **ADD_SYNONYM** (NO_SYNONYM):
  ```sql
  -- [ADD_SYNONYM] {source_keyword} ↔ {target_keyword}
  -- target_keyword_id: {id} (F-4 조회 결과)
  INSERT INTO search_keyword_relations (source_keyword_id, target_keyword_id, relation_type, relation_score)
  VALUES ({src_id}, {tgt_id}, 'SAME', {score});  -- score: F-5 중앙값 참고
  ```

- **FIX_KEYWORD_TYPE** (ETC_TYPE):
  ```sql
  -- [FIX_KEYWORD_TYPE] {keyword}: ETC → {BRAND|CATEGORY}
  UPDATE search_keywords SET keyword_type = '{NEW_TYPE}' WHERE id = {id};
  ```

- **ADD_SIMILAR** (ZERO_NO_MATCH):
  ```sql
  -- [ADD_SIMILAR] {keyword}에 SIMILAR 관계 추가
  INSERT INTO search_keyword_relations (source_keyword_id, target_keyword_id, relation_type, relation_score)
  VALUES ({src_id}, {tgt_id}, 'SIMILAR', {score});
  ```

- **FIX_CATEGORY_MAPPING** (POSSIBLE_FALLBACK — CATEGORY 타입):
  ```sql
  -- [FIX_CATEGORY_MAPPING] {keyword}: search_category_keywords 추가
  INSERT INTO search_category_keywords (search_keyword_id, product_type, search_scope_product_type, requires_name_search)
  VALUES ({keyword_id}, '{product_type}', '{scope}', false);
  ```

- **FIX_BRAND_MAPPING** (POSSIBLE_FALLBACK — BRAND 타입 or BRAND_MAPPING_WRONG):
  ```sql
  -- [FIX_BRAND_MAPPING] {keyword}: brand_id={brand_id} (F-2 조회 결과)
  INSERT INTO search_brand_keywords (search_keyword_id, brand_id) VALUES ({keyword_id}, {brand_id});
  -- 또는 UPDATE search_brand_keywords SET brand_id = {brand_id} WHERE search_keyword_id = {keyword_id};
  ```

SQL 파일 끝:
```sql
COMMIT;
```

NOT_FIXABLE 항목은 SQL 생략, 주석으로만 기록:
